Feature: Report Actions

  Scenario: Export report data in different formats
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    When User clicks on download icon in the grid
    Then User can choose the available formats to export the data

  Scenario: Delete report from My report results screen
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to My report results screen
    When User clicks on any checkbox in the grid
    And User clicks on Delete report in the snackbar
    Then Snackbar displays with the success message "Selected records are deleted"

  Scenario: Delete report from other report results screen
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to other report results screen
    When User clicks on any checkbox in the grid
    And User clicks on Delete report in the snackbar
    Then Snackbar displays with the success message "Selected records are deleted"

  Scenario: Bookmark a report
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to My report results screen
    When User clicks on bookmark icon in the grid
    Then Snackbar displays with the success message

  Scenario: Filter saved reports
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to saved report results screen
    When User clicks on Filter report dropdown
    And User clicks on any dropdown label
    Then User can see the filtered data in the results screen

  Scenario: Delete report from scheduled report results screen
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to Scheduled report results screen
    When User clicks on any checkbox in the grid
    And User clicks on Delete report in the snackbar
    Then Snackbar displays with the success message "Selected records are deleted"

  Scenario: Delete report from saved report results screen
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to saved report results screen
    When User clicks on any checkbox in the grid
    And User clicks on Delete report in the snackbar
    Then Snackbar displays with the success message "Selected records are deleted"

  Scenario: Delete report from other report tab
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to other report tab
    When User clicks on any checkbox in the grid
    And User clicks on Delete report in the snackbar
    Then Snackbar displays with the success message "Selected records are deleted"

  Scenario: Bookmark a report from organize list
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to saved report results screen
    When User clicks on organize list link in the grid header
    And User clicks on bookmark icon in the grid
    Then Snackbar displays with the success message

  Scenario: Bookmark a report directly from saved report results screen
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to saved report results screen
    When User clicks on bookmark icon in the grid
    Then Icon color changes to blue from white

  Scenario: Bookmark a report from bookmarked reports grid
    Given User is on the Report Dashboard
    And User navigates to My Bookmarked Reports grid
    When User clicks on bookmark icon in the grid
    Then Icon color changes to blue from white
